Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Subtitles by: /u/CatZombies \N QC by: Yum and Kolibry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.12,Hamada,,0,0,0,,For the first time on Gaki no Tsukai ya Arahende Chiki Chiki,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.12,0:00:04.90,Hamada,,0,0,0,,making a big reversal from a blunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:08.46,Hamada,,0,0,0,,An apology press conference \N to raise your popularity~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.46,0:00:10.46,Endo,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:11.97,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Ehhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:13.94,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,A bit of a bothersome idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.94,0:00:15.62,Hamada,,0,0,0,,We're doing it. We're doing it so...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:18.08,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Who is going to be fooled by this plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:19.19,Endo,,0,0,0,,Who indeed?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.19,0:00:21.56,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I'm also not really looking forward to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:25.81,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Well, regardless of how much an apology \N press conference increases your popularity,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.81,0:00:27.86,Hamada,,0,0,0,,we're still doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:29.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:31.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Well, if it's about increasing popularity,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:33.51,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,it's no good, not in the slightest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.56,0:00:33.51,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,If you get in trouble, \N you're obligated to do one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.20,0:00:38.92,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I think it's good to learn \N how to do this sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.92,0:00:42.90,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,If you don't do this sort of thing \N often and you play it strangely,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:45.39,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,in a few weeks, it'll be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:48.52,Housei,,0,0,0,,"A lie turned true", that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:49.62,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Scary! Scary!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.62,0:00:51.00,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Scary, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:53.43,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Especially Hamada has got something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:53.43,Hamada,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.43,0:00:55.22,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Even now, he's got many at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:56.65,Hamada,,0,0,0,,No, no, no. There's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.65,0:00:58.65,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's got a bomb, really.
