Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:31.14,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,We're starting with me, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:35.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,First up to bat is Tanaka. \N The details of his uneasy apology are?
