Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:40.76,Endo,,0,0,0,,We already know it, right? The theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.76,0:01:42.76,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's because of that, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:45.91,Endo,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:47.85,Endo,,0,0,0,,Well, it fits his gloomy look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.85,0:01:53.11,Housei,,0,0,0,,If you said someone got caught doing this, \N Tanaka would suddenly come to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.37,0:01:53.11,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Now everyone, Tanaka is first up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:55.85,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Let the apology press conference begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:57.85,Endo,,0,0,0,,This kind of vibe, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.85,0:02:00.37,Endo,,0,0,0,,There's a lot more people than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:08.46,Housei,,0,0,0,,This is pretty good. As expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:10.34,Hamada,,0,0,0,,His face is good!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:10.34,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,His face is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:12.54,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That's an "I messed up" face.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:14.77,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,At this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.77,0:02:16.54,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I caused a lot of trouble and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.54,0:02:18.54,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I am truly and deeply sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:20.88,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:20.88,Endo,,0,0,0,,Good, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:22.72,Endo,,0,0,0,,This is amazingly realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:23.80,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's also about how much you bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:23.80,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.88,0:02:27.36,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Woah, they're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:27.36,Endo,,0,0,0,,Woah, what, what are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.36,0:02:29.23,Endo,,0,0,0,,Makes your heart race.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The crime took place in the middle of the night after 2 a.m. but
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,right before the crime, what on \N earth were you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:41.60,Endo,,0,0,0,,He still doesn't know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:45.04,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yes, ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:47.43,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,As usual, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:48.61,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,work ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:51.35,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I was going home, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:53.10,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,but I was doing so, slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:55.98,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,To exercise my body a little bit, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:58.84,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,"I'll go out", I thought. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're told the scene of the crime was
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the veranda of a second story apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get up on a second story veranda?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:12.06,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yes, ummm, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:17.41,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,This ummm... a little like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:19.44,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,There was this pipe thing. Ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:21.64,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,There was something like a pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:23.57,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Once we watch Tanaka, is it okay if we stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:26.43,Housei,,0,0,0,,We put him through it for about an hour and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:28.82,Housei,,0,0,0,,then "Is it okay if we stop here?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:32.62,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I put my feet on there and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:35.39,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,entered the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's said that you stole several pair of women's underwear that were drying on the veranda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There were underwear drying that were to your liking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:46.67,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,In a nutshell, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:49.08,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:50.66,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's better not to say in a nutshell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:55.06,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Of course, um... well, you can't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:58.01,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I know that but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:02.87,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,As a result, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:02.87,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:05.44,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I became unable to control myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:07.44,Housei,,0,0,0,,No good, you're no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:09.83,Housei,,0,0,0,,The worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.69,Housei,,0,0,0,,That comment was the worst!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, was this the first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, how many times have you done this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:18.57,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is the first time. \N This is really the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:24.12,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Previously, I've not done this sort of thing even once. Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you going to use those underwear for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:30.06,Endo,,0,0,0,,This is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:32.57,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,The truth is, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:34.49,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:36.30,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,My... my own use, so to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,For your own use?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:40.92,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,They'll take pictures for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:44.64,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Do you want to increase your popularity?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:46.31,Housei,,0,0,0,,It's sliding down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:46.31,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,On that note, Tanaka-san, at your house,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,we've heard several thousand pairs of \N women's underwear have been discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Were they all stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:56.57,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Is it not the first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:58.92,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:01.39,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,No, some of them I've bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:03.25,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Bought them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:04.56,Housei,,0,0,0,,He bought them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:07.19,Endo,,0,0,0,,But several thousand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:07.19,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, do you have any final remarks to everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:14.19,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,At this time, um... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:18.01,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,For my troublesome behavior, \N I am truly and deeply sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:21.89,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I've committed a crime. \N Hereafter, as for work, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:23.89,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I'd like to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:23.89,Housei,,0,0,0,,Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:27.05,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,At this time, \N I am truly and deeply sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:29.05,Endo,,0,0,0,,Stealing underwear and putting it on, this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:31.05,Endo,,0,0,0,,Can you do that in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:33.01,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:33.01,Endo,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:34.45,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,No, that's really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:36.04,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:37.24,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Your popularity is ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:39.18,Housei,,0,0,0,,You can't make a comeback.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:39.18,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:41.85,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That wasn't an apology to the person you stole from.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:43.86,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! That's true, isn't it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.56,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Because there's a victim more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:50.28,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,But I stole several thousand pairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.55,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Who do I apologize to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:53.20,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yeah, because you took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:55.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Well, that's right.
