Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.34,0:05:57.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next challenger is Hamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:06:00.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The apology reason is dine and dashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:03.85,Endo,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's really realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:12.56,Housei,,0,0,0,,Wow, wait a minute. This is super realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:15.35,Hamada,,0,0,0,,At this time, \N for the trouble I've caused,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:17.31,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I am truly and deeply sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:21.21,Endo,,0,0,0,,Ah, but he's giving a good face. \N As expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:22.45,Housei,,0,0,0,,His looking down is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:25.64,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,That's right. \N In any case, you can't really see his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada-san, this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:27.53,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it's said this was a midday crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,at roughly what time did it take place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:36.05,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:38.05,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Well, my memory is a little unclear but
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:39.81,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That sort of thing isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:43.82,Hamada,,0,0,0,,midday, 2 p.m. or around 2 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you dine and dash \N at a Kawasaki family restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:49.49,Endo,,0,0,0,,From here, he already understands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:51.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,If you laugh, you're horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:52.95,Housei,,0,0,0,,Just now, he smiled a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:54.08,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He smiled?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:55.75,Housei,,0,0,0,,He smirked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:57.80,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,His lips loosened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.80,0:06:58.84,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:00.08,Endo,,0,0,0,,Ahhh, no good, no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:01.72,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:03.15,Housei,,0,0,0,,That's not crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:06.55,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's thinking. During that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:10.59,Endo,,0,0,0,,No good. If he laughs, it's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:13.65,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't have that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:17.50,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You call it dine and dashing but
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:18.69,Hamada,,0,0,0,,it's not really that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:20.37,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This is the worst denial.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada-san, this your second arrest for dine and dashing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:25.80,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Eh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:28.96,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,He's done this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:31.10,Endo,,0,0,0,,He's done it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.48,0:07:31.10,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I deeply regret this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:33.47,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This guy is the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you recognize that your actions were wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:45.26,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Um, well, I think what I did was bad, but
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:49.76,Hamada,,0,0,0,,dine and dashing? In this era,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:51.58,Hamada,,0,0,0,,you can do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:52.51,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it in these times! You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:56.78,Housei,,0,0,0,,Objectively, he did. Objectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:07:59.92,Hamada,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:03.37,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I'll pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You still haven't apologized to the store owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:09.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:11.49,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no good! No good, no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:12.63,Endo,,0,0,0,,He's getting fed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:15.77,Housei,,0,0,0,,No, what's really going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:18.06,Hamada,,0,0,0,,There's a few differences of opinion, but
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:20.97,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I dine and dashed at a family restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:26.28,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I promise to never do it again and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:28.84,Hamada,,0,0,0,,from the bottom of my heart, \N I'd like to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:31.68,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I am deeply sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:33.61,Endo,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:35.76,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I'm already dumbfounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:38.04,Endo,,0,0,0,,I'm not convinced.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:39.84,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's no Miyane-san. (newscaster)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:42.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I couldn't follow anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:43.44,Housei,,0,0,0,,You couldn't follow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not satisfied with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You ending this press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:53.52,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the heck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:55.64,Endo,,0,0,0,,He's getting fed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:57.64,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Already... hahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:01.61,Endo,,0,0,0,,I hate it, wow. \N That place is rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:02.90,Housei,,0,0,0,,Ehhh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:05.41,Housei,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:07.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.97,Hamada,,0,0,0,,They said I dine and dashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:11.69,Endo,,0,0,0,,Your apology...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:11.69,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,But you didn't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:15.23,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You turned back like this and \N unexpectedly started complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.23,0:09:16.96,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,A lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? \N Do you even understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:23.97,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's laughing too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:29.27,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\p1\fade(0,0)\bord0\shad0\c&H646464&\fscx1566\fscy1948\3c&H000000&\pos(728,530)}m 0 0 l -20 0 l -20 7.6 l 20 10 l 20 0 l 0 0
