Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:29.27,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs85\fade(250,0)\c&H1A00DA&\3c&H000000&\pos(420,710)}Falsification of \N Resume
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:26.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Third up is Endo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:29.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The apology reason is falsification of his resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:38.79,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's like he's kind of making a face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:41.44,Housei,,0,0,0,,That's the face he does for his "Ho ho hoi" gag.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:43.31,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Ahhh, I hate this face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:45.58,Housei,,0,0,0,,I also hate this face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:48.41,Endo,,0,0,0,,At this time, \N for the trouble I've caused,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,0:09:51.92,Endo,,0,0,0,,I am truly and deeply sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.90,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's being theatrical.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:54.57,Housei,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:56.77,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,For your "Bus Hijacking" performance, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:10:00.87,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It was smelly, smelly. \N Really smelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been 27 years since \N you entered show business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.76,0:10:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been deceiving the \N public for a long time but
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,how are you feeling right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:13.16,Endo,,0,0,0,,To the members of the public
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:17.36,Endo,,0,0,0,,and everyone it has affected, my seniors,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:21.44,Endo,,0,0,0,,of course my partner, my family, my juniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:24.85,Endo,,0,0,0,,To everyone that loves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:29.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Juniors that love you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:32.01,Endo,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a problem caused by my own actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:37.28,Endo,,0,0,0,,I made it from nothing, so I'm deeply remorseful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Endo-san, you took up being a sportscaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that was a new challenge but
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that's dead now. How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.17,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Ah, so that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:52.52,Endo,,0,0,0,,That's right. Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:56.44,Endo,,0,0,0,,Since childhood, I've always played baseball and
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:10:59.76,Endo,,0,0,0,,been involved in sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:02.52,Endo,,0,0,0,,Well, to have done this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.52,0:11:05.64,Endo,,0,0,0,,it's really frustrating, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:07.46,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Frustrating?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:07.46,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Endo-san, what is "frustrating"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:12.65,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That's going to be asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:12.65,Housei,,0,0,0,,It's going to be asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's frustrating?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:19.16,Endo,,0,0,0,,Well, rather than myself
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:21.88,Endo,,0,0,0,,everyone that has cared about me, \N wherever they are in society.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:24.08,Endo,,0,0,0,,About those people that I've betrayed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:25.69,Endo,,0,0,0,,it's really frustrating, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:27.20,Housei,,0,0,0,,"Wherever they are in society."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This controversy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're told this originates with Endo-san's last academic career.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you say your high school alma mater was in Shikoku but
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,no school record of you \N was able to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a high school graduate but a middle school graduate, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:44.83,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He's laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:46.83,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:51.00,Endo,,0,0,0,,It's my own inadequacy, but just a little bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:52.97,Endo,,0,0,0,,I wanted to look good, that's what I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:56.99,Endo,,0,0,0,,It was selfish, but I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:12:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,On that note, you've told the story that during your high school senior year,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you served as captain and were \N scouted to play professionally but
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,was this also a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:14.25,Housei,,0,0,0,,He's sweating a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:16.74,Endo,,0,0,0,,That's right. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.74,0:12:20.07,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yeah... it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:25.41,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yeah... yeah it is. \N That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you being a \N Hanshin (baseball) fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:30.58,Endo,,0,0,0,,That too, even now, won't change but
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:33.77,Endo,,0,0,0,,on the other hand, the other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:35.62,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,On the other hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "on the other hand"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:39.42,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It came up. There. \N It came from the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:42.68,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He laughed! He's laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:44.14,Housei,,0,0,0,,He laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:44.14,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.14,0:12:46.71,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Just now, he clearly laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanshin fans...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:48.24,Housei,,0,0,0,,The worst thing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer the previous question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.38,0:12:52.43,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.38,0:12:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What is "on the other hand"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:53.46,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's coming from the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:56.21,Endo,,0,0,0,,I say on the other hand. That...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:59.38,Endo,,0,0,0,,For people like me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:02.60,Endo,,0,0,0,,when it comes to supporting the Tigers,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:05.10,Endo,,0,0,0,,it creates problems and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:09.60,Endo,,0,0,0,,it will create problems for everyone supporting the Tigers, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? \N Do you even understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:17.64,Housei,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:19.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's laughing too much!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. \N Do you have any final words for everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:27.55,Endo,,0,0,0,,From now on, I'll reflect and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:31.28,Endo,,0,0,0,,I really want to do my best with the opportunities that I've been given.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:36.70,Endo,,0,0,0,,This situation is really serious. \N I'm deeply sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:40.43,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,As somewhat expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:43.56,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,A lot of Endo's roughness was apparent in that conference
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:45.28,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You! Don't laugh like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:47.76,Endo,,0,0,0,,I didn't understand what they were asking at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.63,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So that's why you were laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:49.63,Endo,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:54.91,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You could do that laughing \N over and over on "Good Day!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:58.16,Housei,,0,0,0,,Is that good enough? I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:00.50,Housei,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you running away!?
