Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:04.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Fourth up is Housei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:07.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The apology reason is a neighborhood dispute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:14.61,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,His face is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:17.98,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What face is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:20.48,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Well, the feeling isn't good but
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:23.49,Hamada,,0,0,0,,he's making one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:25.48,Housei,,0,0,0,,Eh, at this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:29.23,Housei,,0,0,0,,Everyone, I'm sorry for the \N great troubles I've caused.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.23,0:14:32.44,Housei,,0,0,0,,I am truly and deeply sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:37.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Well, his hair isn't thinning very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to apologize \N to the victims of this affair?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:52.52,Housei,,0,0,0,,Yes. Since then, I've thought \N about it a lot and I'm really
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:54.91,Housei,,0,0,0,,deeply apologetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:15:00.71,Housei,,0,0,0,,From here on, whatever \N I'm able to do, I want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,To go on for 3 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it has been a long and difficult time for your victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:06.25,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He's been doing it for 3 years!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:09.04,Endo,,0,0,0,,That's pretty long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:09.04,Housei,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:12.51,Housei,,0,0,0,,For myself too, thinking about it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:14.90,Housei,,0,0,0,,it feels like it's been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:16.55,Hamada,,0,0,0,,No, he's playing the victim card.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.55,0:15:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What was your grievance with your \N neighbor that started all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:30.13,Housei,,0,0,0,,It was probably the \N neighbor's dog's poop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:34.78,Housei,,0,0,0,,Then, at that time, I cleaned \N up whatever there was but
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:37.80,Housei,,0,0,0,,that became a frequent occurrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:40.98,Housei,,0,0,0,,I gave them a slight warning and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:44.20,Housei,,0,0,0,,there was a bit of a quarrel \N because of that. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:47.19,Housei,,0,0,0,,That's the origin of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Early in the morning, \N you open your window and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,play a boombox at max volume but
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,what sounds were you playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:15:58.67,Housei,,0,0,0,,Well, usually
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:00.65,Housei,,0,0,0,,enka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Enka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was enka? \N In addition to the music,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,it's said you were making strange noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:16.84,Housei,,0,0,0,,I thought by making strange noises, \N I could intimidate the other party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What were the strange noises? \N Could you be more specific?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:27.16,Housei,,0,0,0,,Eh... the strange noises I did then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:29.98,Housei,,0,0,0,,While the music is blaring,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:32.05,Housei,,0,0,0,,"Gyaaa~!!" is what I'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:36.95,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:38.95,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,After he said it, he went "pfff".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,At times, on the neighbor's \N walls and garage
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems you did graffiti in poop but
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.24,0:16:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,what did you write?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.27,Housei,,0,0,0,,"Never erase this."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:55.31,Endo,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you laughing a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a joke to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think this press conference is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:07.80,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Ah, he's laughing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:11.12,Housei,,0,0,0,,I'm deeply sorry. Truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:13.48,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,He apologized!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:16.72,Housei,,0,0,0,,I'm deeply sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:18.12,Housei,,0,0,0,,Is that good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel you're being sincere. \N Don't end this on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:25.20,Endo,,0,0,0,,He said "Is that good enough?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:27.87,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Saying "Is that good enough?" is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.10,0:17:31.24,Housei,,0,0,0,,I'm deeply sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:33.73,Housei,,0,0,0,,I'm deeply sorry. Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:35.68,Housei,,0,0,0,,Is that good enough? I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, a few words to everyone please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.15,0:17:38.28,Housei,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:40.26,Housei,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:41.81,Endo,,0,0,0,,He's ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:46.60,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You can't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:48.27,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,He ran away. He ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:50.89,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That was no good. As expected,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:52.82,Hamada,,0,0,0,,he laughed and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:55.03,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He laughed for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:55.03,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:57.34,Endo,,0,0,0,,That was the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:58.44,Housei,,0,0,0,,No, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:18:00.59,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,No, it's your own remarks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:03.29,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Ending the press conference yourself, \N that's definitely no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:05.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Saying "Is that good enough?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:08.00,Housei,,0,0,0,,"Is that good enough?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Tie your necktie properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:12.66,Endo,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:14.90,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,They're going to say that.
