Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:19.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Last is Matsumoto, who also \N has a job as a commentator.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:22.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The apology reason is indecent exposure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:30.74,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He's looking somewhat self-important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:34.63,Housei,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. \N Shouldn't he straighten his tie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:39.43,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Why did he loosen his collar and necktie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:39.43,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,At this time, for the trou...ble I've caused,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:40.98,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I'm truly and deeply sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:42.26,Housei,,0,0,0,,He stuttered!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:43.95,Housei,,0,0,0,,Hamada, he fumbled over his words.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:46.34,Hamada,,0,0,0,,His tie is loose and he's fumbling his words.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:52.20,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Pay attention to your tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto-san, when you were arrested, it seems you were hiding your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:59.05,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yes, ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:00.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I don't get his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:06.08,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,"That was embarrassing", I thought. My own actions, those were embarrassing, so
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:11.12,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,"I can't show my face to everyone", I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:14.06,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, you were naked \N hanging around in a park
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and a passing couple reported you, \N resulting in you getting arrested, but
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,why did you do those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:29.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yes. Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:31.87,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Publicly, that definitely isn't
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:34.72,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,acceptable, I understand that but
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.72,0:19:38.71,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,in regards to being naked... to do that um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:40.02,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I had no ill intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.02,0:19:45.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,About that, my thoughts on \N being naked are, that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:48.62,Endo,,0,0,0,,Huh? Huh? \N I don't really understand what he means.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:49.84,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He hasn't apologized at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:52.81,Housei,,0,0,0,,He's losing his composure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a celebrity so \N what you did was okay!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:55.72,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Ah, here he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:57.81,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Sorry, ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.81,0:20:03.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm a celebrity so, of course, I need to use common sense and
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:06.72,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I always have those feelings but
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:11.17,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,perhaps those feelings became \N too strong and due to stress
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:12.77,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I did those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an excuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:16.08,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yes, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:18.90,Housei,,0,0,0,,Apologize sincerely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The one you were arrested \N at was Komazawa Park but
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.37,0:20:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,At Komazawa Park, we've heard that you decided on a circular route but
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,what route was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.63,0:20:33.81,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Generally, that was the marathon course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The marathon course?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:37.11,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,There's a marathon course, but
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:39.30,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I was going in the opposite direction around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:43.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,When passing by the people doing the marathon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the information \N from when you were arrested,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're told that Matsumoto-san had phimosis. \N Is this true?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:55.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yes. I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.18,0:20:58.65,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Tightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tightly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:02.31,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He laughed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:02.31,Endo,,0,0,0,,Ah, he laughed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:05.01,Housei,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:06.58,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,He's laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything you'd like to say to your partner Hamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:14.88,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yes, um, we've really been \N together since elementary school,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:18.72,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,at Yoshimoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.72,0:21:22.99,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Since he was also the one that proposed we work together, really in regards to him
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:25.42,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I'm really, deeply sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:28.28,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I really hope everyone can get past this, despite what Hamada's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:29.59,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Hey, what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.59,0:21:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This means you're going to quit too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to quit show business?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.17,0:21:37.46,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Hamada
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:40.64,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,must stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.64,0:21:42.22,Housei,,0,0,0,,That's really the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.22,0:21:43.62,Endo,,0,0,0,,It's the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:45.56,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the heck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:47.39,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He's laughing so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.39,0:21:51.28,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Wait, if I think about Hamada's \N feelings, I can't say anything more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:53.59,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I don't know. Please ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.93,0:21:58.17,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the heck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:22:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, is there anything \N you'd like to tell everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.82,0:22:06.19,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yes, well, people after all
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.19,0:22:13.08,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,can't exactly go out without \N wearing clothes, I've learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.08,0:22:16.28,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That I really understand and
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.28,0:22:19.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I hope to let Hamada know as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.04,0:22:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, about that last thing you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.83,0:22:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,does that mean Hamada-san \N also often goes out in the nude?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.31,0:22:27.25,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,No, sorry. I have no comment about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.25,0:22:28.05,Hamada,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.05,0:22:31.17,Housei,,0,0,0,,Something like "no comment" isn't \N okay at an apology press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.17,0:22:31.78,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an apology press conference! You can't say no comment at an apology press conference!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.47,0:22:36.03,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.03,0:22:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Hamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.57,0:22:40.65,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That guy is really
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.65,0:22:41.53,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,that sort of guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.53,0:22:45.30,Hamada,,0,0,0,,No, what sort... what sort of stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:46.52,Housei,,0,0,0,,He's laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.60,0:22:46.52,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:47.38,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He's laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:22:50.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:52.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.71,0:22:54.27,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:22:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much. \N Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.17,0:22:59.17,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.74,0:23:02.04,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Stop already. \N After all that, bowing that deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.04,0:23:05.18,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Take care of that necktie already.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.18,0:23:07.02,Housei,,0,0,0,,That really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.02,0:23:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tie your necktie properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.45,0:23:12.30,Endo,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.30,0:23:14.13,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,They're going to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:16.84,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That's no good. This is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.84,0:23:19.91,Endo,,0,0,0,,Come on, like that guy says.
